# JSON Parser Project Overview

This is a modern JSON parser and formatter web application built with Next.js 14, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS. The project provides real-time JSON parsing, validation, formatting, and visualization with a beautiful tree view.

## Key Features
- Real-time JSON parsing and validation
- Beautiful syntax highlighting with collapsible tree view
- Auto-format JSON data with escape character handling
- Download and copy functionality
- Timestamp converter utility
- User-friendly error messages

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 14 with App Router
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui components
- **Icons**: Lucide React + FontAwesome
- **Testing**: Jest with React Testing Library
- **JSON Processing**: jsonrepair library

## Main Entry Points
- [app/page.tsx](mdc:app/page.tsx) - Main application page
- [app/layout.tsx](mdc:app/layout.tsx) - Root layout with global styles
- [app/components/JsonParser.tsx](mdc:app/components/JsonParser.tsx) - Core JSON parser component

